app_name: Groups Control Groups Messenger Apps Tzp
app_description: TZP is a mobile messaging app that helps you easily connect with friends around the world. TZP can be used for group chats voice chats and calls allowing you to experience a convenient mobile lifestyle. Why use Tzp: Cross platform: Supports synchronization and sending of messages on desktop and mobile phones Multimedia: Messages such as pictures text voice and video are supported. Group chat: You can form a group chat with 200 people. Voice Chat: Deliver high quality calls across the globe. Virtual number: Provides high quality calls to users around the world around the clock. Privacy protection: We strictly protect the privacy and security of users and real time messages are encrypted.
